Accessibility
- Use semantic elements; ensure form controls have labels.
- Provide keyboard support and visible focus states.
- Prefer `aria-*` only when semantics are insufficient.

UX
- Include loading and empty states for all async views.
- Avoid layout shift; reserve space for async content.

